author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
DISEASE is spreading in the world of AoS as the children of Grandfather Nurgle are unleashed once again on the Mortal Realms, backed up by new models and the characters from Warhammer Quest: Darkwater. Let's check it out!

Big thanks to GW for a complimentary copy of the book and boxes to review.
